<h1>Dedicated vs VPS Hosting</h1>
<p>What are the differences between a dedicated server and a VPS? Which one is right for you?</p>

<p>Some advantages of a dedicated server over a VPS include:</p>

<ul>
    <li>No shared resources</li>
    <li>Full control</li>
    <li>Improved performance</li>
</ul>
<h3>No Shared Resources</h3>
<p>With a dedicated server, all of the hardware specs are yours to use. Resources are not shared with any other users since there are no other users on the machine. There are no virtual drives or containers for other people to use.</p>
{% endblock %}

