<p>Since there are no shared resources and you cannot affect others with applications you want to install, you can install any applications as you see fit. You can take the dedicated server to its limits and not worry about limiting your application or website.</p>

<h3>Full Control</h3>
<p>With root access, you can modify the server as you want when you want it. Modify server side files and change system settings to cater to what you need to do.</p>

<h3>Improved Performance</h3>
<p>Since the server is all yours and you have full control of how programs behave, server performance is faster. You also do not need to worry about the server slowing severly because of a VPS constumer heavily loading the CPU and RAM.</p>
